<title>Best Black Friday Deals NOT Found on Amazon</title>
<link>http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-black-friday-deals-not-amazon/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-black-friday-deals-not-amazon/</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;Thanksgiving approaches faster than a turkey running away from the chopping block. Or that sense of foreboding that goes hand in hand with familial visits. With it comes Black Friday for unbelievable deals. Whether you’re shopping for yourself or holiday shopping for friends and family, these are the best Black Friday deals around.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; Some of these deals won’t be available until Black Friday begins at 12am EST on November 24, 2017.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://cdn.makeuseof.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2979994-500x500.jpeg?x16845&quot; alt=&quot;LG-43UJ6300-Black-Friday&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;500&quot;/&gt;Image Credit: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kohls.com/product/prd-2979994/lg-43-inch-2160p-4k-ultra-hd-hdr-smart-tv-43uj6300.jsp&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Kohl’s&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;Kohl’s may not rank among the most well-known electronics retailers like Best Buy. Nevertheless, Kohl’s will offer many of Black Friday 2017’s top deals. The LG 49UJ6300 smart TV features an IPS panel, webOS Smart Platform, and 2160P resolution. Plus, there’s HDR. The LG 49UJ6300 retails for a regular price of $700, so its &lt;a href=&quot;http://tgiblackfriday.com/Kohls/Haier-55-4K-HDTV-90-Kohl-s-Cash-deal&quot;&gt;discounted price of $400&lt;/a&gt; is an &lt;em&gt;incredible&lt;/em&gt; value. Additionally, Kohl’s offers a promotion where consumers gain $15 in Kohl’s cash for each $50 spent. As such, the LG affords $120 in Kohl’s cash for a net price of $280. It’s tough to beat that price for an HDR 4K IPS panel.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;Alternatively, Kohl’s also sells the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kohls.com/product/prd-3040562/haier-55-in-4k-ultra-hd-led-tv-55ug2500.jsp&quot;&gt;Haier 55-inch 4K LED&lt;/a&gt;. It’s a 4K Ultra HD LED with 120 Hz refresh rate, four HDMI inputs, and a large 55-inch screen. At $300 plus $90 back in Kohl’s cash for a net price of $210, it’s a solid deal. But the LG, despite its smaller screen real estate, boasts HDR which makes it a better choice. Over at Best Buy, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bestbuy.com/site/insignia-39-class-38-5-diag--led-1080p-smart-hdtv-roku-tv/4863802.p&quot;&gt;there’s a 39-inch Insignia panel&lt;/a&gt; on sale for $179, down from $279. While it’s only a 1080p set, not 4K, that’s a ridiculous deal for a TV of this size.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://cdn.makeuseof.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/google-home-mini-1-670x398.jpg?x16845&quot; alt=&quot;google home mini black friday&quot; width=&quot;670&quot; height=&quot;398&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;Expect massive discounts on smart home gadgets, like the Amazon Echo or Google Home Mini (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-assistant-siri-smart-ai/&quot;&gt;best personal assistant&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-assistant-siri-smart-ai/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Why Google Assistant Is a Better Smart AI Than Apple’s Siri&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-info&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-title&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-assistant-siri-smart-ai/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Why Google Assistant Is a Better Smart AI Than Apple’s Siri&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-excerpt&quot;&gt;Siri may have been the pioneering voice assistant on a smartphone, but it’s been years since most of us took her seriously. Are other voice assistants simply better? Let's take a look.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-assistant-siri-smart-ai/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; ). On Black Friday, Target will &lt;a href=&quot;https://bestblackfriday.com/ads/target-black-friday&quot;&gt;discount the Google Home Mini to $29&lt;/a&gt;, down from its regular price of $49. On top of that, the Home Mini comes with a $10 Target gift card, lowering the price to a net of $19. You can’t beat this price for an affordable smart assistant.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;Aside from the Google Home Mini, Target discounts several smart home speakers and hubs. You’ll also find the Amazon Echo for $80 and the Echo Show for $180, both all-time low prices. Best Buy also lowers the price of the Google Home Mini to $29 and throws in a $10 Best Buy gift card (with purchase). Debating purchasing a Google Home device? &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-home-device-questions/&quot;&gt;Learn more about Google Home&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-home-device-questions/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Want a New Google Home Device? 7 Questions to Ask Before You Buy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-info&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-title&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-home-device-questions/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Want a New Google Home Device? 7 Questions to Ask Before You Buy&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-excerpt&quot;&gt;Google's new Google Home smart speakers, Nest Hello doorbell, and the Google Clips camera are getting a lot of buzz. But before you make a purchase, ask yourself these questions!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/google-home-device-questions/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://cdn.makeuseof.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Roku-streaming-box-670x335.jpg?x16845&quot; alt=&quot;roku premiere black friday&quot; width=&quot;670&quot; height=&quot;335&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;Streaming is all the rage, and while the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-android-tv-box/&quot;&gt;Nvidia Shield TV is the best Android TV box&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-android-tv-box/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Best Android TV Box on the Planet for All Budgets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-info&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-title&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-android-tv-box/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Best Android TV Box on the Planet for All Budgets&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-excerpt&quot;&gt;Looking for the best Android TV Box on the planet? Moe Long rounds up the top three Android TV boxes around, for budget, midrange, and high-end needs!&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-android-tv-box/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; , the Roku reigns supreme. &lt;a href=&quot;http://variety.com/2017/digital/news/roku-market-share-1202538133/&quot;&gt;Roku’s market share&lt;/a&gt; continues to outstrip that of competitors such as Apple. The Roku Premiere+ is the Roku set-top box to buy. It sports 4K capabilities and includes an Ethernet port. If you’re streaming in 4K, you’ll want to use a hardwired connection rather than Wi-Fi. The Premiere+ is one of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-plex-clients-streaming-media/&quot;&gt;best Plex client devices&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&qu