nge, high-end, and DIY.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-media-streaming-device/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; as well. Rather than a smart TV, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/buy-roku-not-smart-tv/&quot;&gt;grab a Roku&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/buy-roku-not-smart-tv/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Don't Buy a Smart TV -- Buy a Roku Instead&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-info&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-title&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/buy-roku-not-smart-tv/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Don't Buy a Smart TV -- Buy a Roku Instead&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-excerpt&quot;&gt;Stop! Don't buy that smart TV. Instead, read this article and find out why it would be better to buy a dumb TV plus a standalone streaming device to go with it.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/buy-roku-not-smart-tv/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
