&lt;p&gt;Although the iPhone X, 8, and 8 Plus are superb devices, better phones for the money are available. As such, the iPhone SE is arguably the best Black Friday phone deal for Apple buffs. Its’s one of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnet.com/products/apple-iphone-se-review/&quot;&gt;best phones&lt;/a&gt; among Apple gadgets. The SE is essentially an iPhone 6 crammed into the form factor of an iPhone 5. For Black Friday, Target cuts the price to $100, which is $60 less than its normal retail value. This is the 32GB variant, but for a no-contract phone this is one of the top mobile deals you’ll find. Alternately, check out the Moto G5Ss on sale for $225 unlocked from Best Buy.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
