&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;aligncenter&quot; src=&quot;http://cdn.makeuseof.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/JBL-Charge-3.jpg?x16845&quot; alt=&quot;JBL Charge 3 Macy's Black Friday&quot; width=&quot;300&quot; height=&quot;167&quot;/&gt;Image Credit: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01F24RHF4/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Amazon&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-bluetooth-speakers-25-300-2016/&quot;&gt;JBL makes many of the best rated&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-bluetooth-speakers-25-300-2016/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Best Bluetooth Speakers Under $25 and up to $300 in 2016&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-info&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-title&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-bluetooth-speakers-25-300-2016/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Best Bluetooth Speakers Under $25 and up to $300 in 2016&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-excerpt&quot;&gt;You can't beat the convenience of going wire-free. Great audio quality may always need wired speakers, but for music on your phone Bluetooth speakers are a must-have accessory nowadays.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/best-bluetooth-speakers-25-300-2016/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; speakers available. Its Charge 3 is a waterproof speaker which boasts luscious sound quality in a portable package. For Black Friday 2017, the Charge 3 comes down to $90. Normally, the Charge 3 retails for $150. Notably, Target and Best Buy both discount the JBL Charge 3 to $90 as well.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
