&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/chromebook-makeuseof-explains/&quot;&gt;Chromebooks are nifty&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/chromebook-makeuseof-explains/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;What Is A Chromebook? [MakeUseOf Explains]&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-info&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-title&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/chromebook-makeuseof-explains/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;What Is A Chromebook? [MakeUseOf Explains]&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-excerpt&quot;&gt;Everything is moving towards the web, which is now more commonly being dubbed “the cloud”. As such, your devices should probably be ready and well equipped to make full use of cloud services for your...&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/chromebook-makeuseof-explains/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; little devices. The super portable netbook successors are much more functional than their predecessors in the tiny laptop niche. They travel well, and it’s simple to &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/install-linux-chromebook/&quot;&gt;install Linux on most Chromebooks&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/install-linux-chromebook/&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;How to Install Linux on a Chromebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-info&quot;&gt;&l