<og:type>article</og:type>
<og:description>Adobe Acrobat Pro DC is Adobe's newest PDF editor. But does a free alternative like PDFescape offer all the features you need? We'll find out.</og:description>
<og:image>http://cdn.makeuseof.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/free-pdf-editor-adobe-994x400.jpg?x16845</og:image>
