<item>
<title>Looking to Do Some Shopping? Here Are Some Great Deals for You</title>
<link>http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/looking-shopping-great-deals/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/looking-shopping-great-deals/</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;Today, you can get great deals on a waterproof Bluetooth speaker, a carpet cleaner, a TomTom fitness watch, PC gaming accessories, and much more!&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
