&lt;p&gt;Timberlake’s Twitter page mostly consists of pictures and quips about his various activities. He posts pictures of concerts, other bands he wants to promote, and causes he supports. Recently, he announced on Twitter that he’ll be performing at the Super Bowl LII halftime show.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
