&lt;h2&gt;7. Lady Gaga (@ladygaga)&lt;/h2&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Followers:&lt;/strong&gt; 72.4 million | &lt;strong&gt;Following:&lt;/strong&gt; 129k | &lt;strong&gt;Tweets:&lt;/strong&gt; 8,548&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
&lt;p&gt;Stefani Joanne Angelina Germanotta, better known by her stage name Lady Gaga, is everyone’s favorite freakshow. In 2008, she released her first album &lt;em&gt;The Fame&lt;/em&gt;, which included the big single “Poker Face.” Several albums and hit singles later, she’s one of the best-selling artists of all time. She also regularly engages in charitable work.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
