rth It?)&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;link-callout-excerpt&quot;&gt;There are many Twitter users with blue tick marks next to their name. The blue tick denotes a verified account, meaning this is a real person and is whoever their description says it is.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.makeuseof.com/tag/how-to-get-a-verified-account-on-twitter-and-is-it-worth-it/&quot; class=&quot;link-callout-link&quot; onclick=&quot;ga('send','event','ui','link-callout');&quot;&gt;Read More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
